cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.SI 

This paper deals with natural language processing and computer vision, which are both subfields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on modeling the understanding of other agents and adapting to novel gameplay partners suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and social intelligence (cs.SI). The use of image datasets and reference games suggests a focus on computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
